  "conclusion": "L8 c2 per_row_preqkv_append_context_gate_batch_o_post_moe is hidden/token green while keeping batch O, batch post-attention, and grouped_compact MoE. The same pre-QKV+append sequence with batch context/gate is hidden-red, and the per-row context + batch gate split is also hidden-red. Therefore the C2.3 green boundary requires per-row context+gate (after per-row pre-QKV/append) before batch O/post/MoE; batch O/post/MoE remain eliminated. Active full c2 verify varied across two post-change runs (82 then 137), so no runtime default or throughput/scaling claim is made.",
